{
  "stem": "26728.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was just before we left-- the day or so before we left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The way they used the gas-- and I said-- I said, well, there's got to be a-- you know, where's the-- where's the faucet?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where's the handle?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There has to be a handle they turn it on with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was thinking of, I don't know, carbon monoxide or something like that, some way to get gas inside that room, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A pump or something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said hell no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's not what works.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, what they do-- those-- those shower heads don't go any place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just are fastened to the wall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's no pipes connected to them at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and this man that explained it to him, who spoke English and showed it to me too, he said the same thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went back in and-- and looked at it again, and he couldn't-- if you didn't really inspect it, you wouldn't even notice this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you can-- then he showed us the shaft, and he said they'd-- they take-- the-- the guy, the SS man has a mask on, has a gas mask on, and protective gloves and everything, and a screwdriver.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Zyklon B comes in a can-- a canister with a lid that you have to pry off like a paint can.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's pressurized, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It has-- you can't get it off accidentally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to pry it all the way around like a can of paint.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he dumps the crystals in these slots, which drop down into the inside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as soon as they hit the air, they release the cyanide gas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what kills people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how this one worked.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
